parameters.description:
Call this tool to perform a reverse image search. Reverse image searches return urls where similar looking products exists. Fetch the returned urls to gather more information. This tool requires the following object request body.
```
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "image_url": { "type": "string" },
   }
}
```
image_url should be an absolute URL to the image.

Call this tool to retrieve page contents of a url.
```
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "url": { "type": "string" },
   }
}
```
url should be an absolute URL.
